{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/block-opening-brace-newline-before/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/block-closing-brace-space-before/","description":"block-opening-brace-newline-after 要求在块的开大括号之后必须有换行符。 此规则允许行尾注释后跟换行符。例如： 有关将此规则与block-opening-brace-newline-before 一起使用的更多信息，请参阅常见问题禁止单行规则。…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"block-opening-brace-newline-after\"><a href=\"#block-opening-brace-newline-after\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>block-opening-brace-newline-after</h1>\n<p>要求在块的开大括号之后必须有换行符。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n    ↑ <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑\n * 这个大括号之后的换行符 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则允许行尾注释后跟换行符。例如：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 行尾注释 */</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>有关将此规则与<a href=\"../block-opening-brace-newline-before/\"><code>block-opening-brace-newline-before</code></a> 一起使用的更多信息，请参阅<a href=\"../../../../user-guide/faq/#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%95%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97\">常见问题</a>禁止单行规则。</p>\n<p><a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\">命令行</a>中的 <code>--fix</code> 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的所有问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"always\"|\"always-multi-line\"|\"never-multi-line\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"always\"><a href=\"#always\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"always\"</code></h3>\n<p>在开大括号之后<em>必须</em>有一个换行符。</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>{ <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>{ <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>{ <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 包含换行符的\n    行尾注释 */</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>\n{\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 行尾注释 */</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"always-multi-line\"><a href=\"#always-multi-line\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"always-multi-line\"</code></h3>\n<p>在多行块的开大括号之后<em>必须</em>有一个换行符。</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span>{<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"never-multi-line\"><a href=\"#never-multi-line\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"never-multi-line\"</code></h3>\n<p>在多行块的开大括号之后<em>不能</em>有空白符。</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/block-opening-brace-newline-after.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/block-opening-brace-newline-after/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/block-opening-brace-newline-after/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/block-opening-brace-newline-after/index.html.aef1378bf0d52c51b0049832d8193f2d.json"}